# labels

**Instance Property**

A set of labels present in the dataset.

## Declaration

```swift
var labels: Set<Label>
```

## Getting the properties Properties

- **defaultConfidenceThreshold**: The default confidence threshold. It is used as the confidence threshold for any label which does not have an explicit confidence threshold, while calculating averagePrecision and meanAveragePrecision.
